format: A data frame with 625 observations on the following 8 variables.
description:
Description
Data on genetic variation in responses to fertilization
and simulated herbivory in Arabidopsis
title: Arabidopsis clipping/fertilization data

parameters.rack:
a nuisance factor with 2 levels, one for
each of two greenhouse racks
parameters.status:
a nuisance factor for germination method
(Normal, Petri.Plate, or Transplant)
parameters.reg:
region: a factor with 3 levels NL
(Netherlands), SP (Spain), SW (Sweden)
parameters.popu:
population: a factor with the form n.R
representing a population in region R
parameters.amd:
simulated herbivory or "clipping" (apical meristem
damage): unclipped (baseline) or clipped
parameters.nutrient:
fertilization treatment/nutrient level (1,
minimal nutrients or 8, added nutrients)
